@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rmxysb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.71 * tmp + 0.76)) + 0.32)
    v0 = (v2 / wp.abs(0.84))
    v1 = ((tmp + wp.cos(v0 + 0.58)) * (wp.cos(v0 + 0.01) / v0))
    v0 = ((0.72 * v2) - wp.cos(v2))
    v0 = v0
    v2 = (0.12 - v1)
    v0 = (wp.exp(0.62) / wp.exp((tmp + 0.69 * v2 + 0.98)))
    data[tid] = v0
